oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Hank Williams: Complete Works Volume 1
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: The recording is of a number of performances of Hank Williams Sr. (singer/songwriter). Tape is part of a collection labeled Hank Williams: Complete Works. Tape is labeled as part one of eight. The tapes were donated from the M.G.M. Studios collection.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Hank Williams
